閱讀並理解中級至中高級(intermediate ~high intermediate level)英文文章。','This is a two-credit, one-semester course. Included in the instruction for students of all levels are grammar review, basic sentence structure, introduction and application of English reading skills to high-intermediate reading articles, outlining and summarizing, as well as general or professional conversational English, talks, lectures, reports, and programs.','1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放健科學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。','全18週',1132,'21140','1','通識必修(通識)','4','1,2','F605','22',2),('2310','專題研究','Independent Study','本課程以個別指導之形式，依據碩士生之護理專長背景及未來專業發展方向，引導學生探索相關核心概念、理論，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，訂定研究方向及主題，擬定研究設計、完成研究計畫之書寫。','This course is delivered in an individualized format, tailored to the nursing specialization and future professional development of the master\'s student. It guides students in exploring relevant core concepts and theories, integrating their clinical expertise, applying critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, determining research directions and topics, and developing research designs, culminating in the completion of a research proposal.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（兒童組一般生）、書面選課','全18週',1141,'11166','2','專業選修(系所)','7','1','','A0',1),('2311','專題研究','Independent Study','本課程旨在幫助學生對未來論文撰述之相關議題做更深入完備之探討。課程中，學生必須與該專業領域相關專長之教師共同訂訂學習契約並透過輔導達成學習目標。','The purpose of this course is to help students to gain knowledge related to an identified research topic. The student will be evaluated based on the pre-arranged learning objectives in the learning contract.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授。修課限制：本所碩士班（婦女組一般生）、書面選課','全18週',1141,'11163','2','專業選修(系所)','7','1','','A0',1),('2312','專題研究','Independent Study','本課程以個別指導之形式，依據碩士生之護理專長背景及未來專業發展方向，引導學生探索相關核心概念、理論，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，訂定研究方向及主題，擬定研究設計、完成研究計畫之書寫。','This course is delivered in an individualized format, tailored to the nursing specialization and future professional development of the master\'s student. It guides students in exploring relevant core concepts and theories, integrating their clinical expertise, applying critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, determining research directions and topics, and developing research designs, culminating in the completion of a research proposal.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（老人組一般生）、書面選課','全18週',1141,'11162','2','專業選修(系所)','7','1','','A0',1),('2313','碩士論文','Thesis','本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助碩士生以臨床實務為基礎，應用護理理論及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析，並完成研究成果報告及碩士論文之撰寫。','This course is structured as individualized instruction, aiming to assist the master\'s student in utilizing clinical practice as a foundation. It focuses on the application of nursing theory and research skills, the execution of research protocol, data analysis, and the completion of research outcome reports and the master\'s thesis.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（兒童組一般生）、書面選課','全18週',1141,'11166','2','專業必修(系所)','7','2','','A0',6),('2314','碩士論文','Thesis','本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助碩士生以臨床實務為基礎，應用護理理論及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析，並完成研究成果報告及碩士論文之撰寫。','This course is structured as individualized instruction, aiming to assist the master\'s student in utilizing clinical practice as a foundation. It focuses on the application of nursing theory and research skills, the execution of research protocol, data analysis, and the completion of research outcome reports and the master\'s thesis.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（護資組一般生）、書面選課','全18週',1141,'11167','2','專業必修(系所)','7','2','','A0',6),('2315','碩士論文','Thesis','本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助碩士生以臨床實務為基礎，應用護理理論及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析，並完成研究成果報告及碩士論文之撰寫。','This course is structured as individualized instruction, aiming to assist the master\'s student in utilizing clinical practice as a foundation. It focuses on the application of nursing theory and research skills, the execution of research protocol, data analysis, and the completion of research outcome reports and the master\'s thesis.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所碩士班（社區組一般生）、書面選課','全18週',1141,'11165','2','專業必修(系所)','7','2','','A0',6),('2316','碩士論文','Thesis','本課程以個別指導之形式，