ourse includes a two-hour aural-oral drill in the language laboratory each week. Students are placed to different levels according to their individual English ability displayed in a placement test administered beforehand.  The main contents of the course are listening and speaking skills of intermediate to high intermediate level.  Students are requested to practice pronunciation skills and pass the sequential oral tests.','1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。','全18週',1132,'31140','1','通識必修(通識)','3','1,2','F610','11',1),('56','質性研究','Qualitative Research','本課程旨在提供學生認識質性研究及其在護理上的運用。課程內容包括質性研究概念的介紹、研究設計、資料的收集與詮釋、以及報告的撰寫。本課程藉由課堂講授，輔以論文研討等方式帶領學生認識質性研究方法，並探討其在應用上的重要議題，以輔助學生在閱讀及使用質性研究方法的能力','This course focuses on the basic of qualitative research and its applications in the nursing field. The contents of this course include qualitative respective on research, qualitative research design, qualitative data collection and analysis, and qualitat','修課限制：\n1.本所開放兩組選課，限18人。\n2.外所本國生3名。','全18週',1132,'33161','1','專業選修(系所)','2','3,4','IB02','10',2),('560','英文二','Freshman English II','本課程包括每週兩小時的閱讀。教學重點為文法重點複習、閱讀技巧及練習，普通英文閱讀。於該課程中學生能熟練基本文法重點，學習並運用各種英文閱讀技巧，閱讀並理解初中級～中級(low-intermediate ~ intermediate level) 普通英文文章。','This course includes a two-hour reading instruction each week. Students are placed to different levels according to their individual English ability displayed in a placement test administered beforehand.  Teaching materials covered, therefore, will differ in order to meet the needs of students of different levels.  The main contents of the course are grammar review, reading skills and practice in low-intermediate or intermediate level general English.','1.建議同學依排定時程修習課程避免延畢，如遇特殊原因須停修者，須先至通識中心進行前置流程。2.第二階段加退選開放人康學院重修生選課。3.第三階段加退選開放系外重修生選課。','全18週',1132,'31140','1','通識必修(通識)','3','3,4','B216','12',2),('561','英語聽講練習二','Freshman English Lab II','本課程包括每週2小時1學分的英語聽與講練習。學生經程度測驗後依程度分級。教學重點為初中級～中高級(intermediate to high intermediate 