 or healing environment and the different groups that make use of health promotion or healing environment.','修課限制：本系四技一般生大三以上、本所','全18週',1132,'23140','3','專業必修(系所)','4','6,7','F902','A0',2),('970','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','5','6,7,8,9','G101','B0',3),('971','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','1','6,7,8,9','G204','C0',3),('972','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','2','1,2,3,4','G204','C0',3),('973','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','3','6,7,8,9','G204','C0',3),('974','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','4','1,2,3,4','G204','C0',3),('975','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','2','6,7,8,9','G101','D0',3),('976','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing process to identify clients’ health problems and implement feasible nursing interventions to meet the needs of clients during simulation and Objective Structured Clinical Examination (OSCE).','修課限制：本系四技一般生大四、護理系學士後大三、畢業班課程、不開放自行加退或換班','第8~14週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','3','1,2,3,4','G101','D0',3),('977','綜合實作','Integrated clinical practice','本課程旨在強化學生綜合護理實務應用的能力，課室內容包括各科情境模擬演練與評測。','This course is designed to enhance students’ nursing competence. Students could learn to apply critical thinking and nursing 