化其心肺功能。授課內容為救生自救觀\r\n念、捷泳、仰泳、蝶泳，期望能成為學生的終身運動項目。','The course is to have students learn correct swimming skills and poses and \r\nestablish the ability and concept of self rescue in the water and strengthen \r\ntheir cardio-pulmonary function through the process of learning various \r\nswimming skills. Curriculum includes self rescue concepts, front crawl, \r\nbackstroke, butterfly stroke in to hope of making swimming a lifelong exercise \r\nitem for the students.','1.第一階段志願選，僅由護二一Ｄ、護二一Ｃ、休四三Ａ互相跨班選課。\n2.第二階段加退選，開放全校二技一般生及四技一般生選課。\n3.上課地點請洽體育室，一學期至多修習2門必修體育。','全18週',1132,'23140','3','通識必修(通識)','3','6,7','','A0',0),('980','臨床就業選習','Practicum for Obtaining Nursing Employment','本課程旨在培養學生整合並運用專業護理相關之知識與技能，於護理實務工作中，透過連續性且全時臨床護理實習，增加學生職場就業機會及提升工作適應能力，以奠定學生從事臨床護理工作的基礎。','The purpose of the course is to develop students’ clinical competence in hospital settings. Within the practicum, students will be trained to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in daily nursing practice. The training contents include practicing nursing routings, writing nursing records, familiar with nursing staff job descriptions, and participating in managing emergency situations. Students are expected to provide evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care based on assessment. Students will also be trained to communicate and cooperate with other medical team members, and to provide patients and their families health education and consultation. Students are also encouraged to actively participating in clinical and ethical issue discussions.','實習期間：02/19-04/03，修課限制：實習課程、本系四技一般生大四、畢業班課程、修課名單由護理系實習辦公室提供','第1~7週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','2','1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9','','L0',6),('981','臨床就業選習','Practicum for Obtaining Nursing Employment','本課程旨在培養學生整合並運用專業護理相關之知識與技能，於護理實務工作中，透過連續性且全時臨床護理實習，增加學生職場就業機會及提升工作適應能力，以奠定學生從事臨床護理工作的基礎。','The purpose of the course is to develop students’ clinical competence in hospital settings. Within the practicum, students will be trained to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in daily nursing practice. The training contents include practicing nursing routings, writing nursing records, familiar with nursing staff job descriptions, and participating in managing emergency situations. Students are expected to provide evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care based on assessment. Students will also be trained to communicate and cooperate with other medical team members, and to provide patients and their families health education and consultation. Students are also encouraged to actively participating in clinical and ethical issue discussions.','實習期間：02/19-04/03，修課限制：實習課程、本系四技一般生大四、畢業班課程、修課名單由護理系實習辦公室提供','第1~7週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','3','1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9','','L0',6),('982','臨床就業選習','Practicum for Obtaining Nursing Employment','本課程旨在培養學生整合並運用專業護理相關之知識與技能，於護理實務工作中，透過連續性且全時臨床護理實習，增加學生職場就業機會及提升工作適應能力，以奠定學生從事臨床護理工作的基礎。','The purpose of the course is to develop students’ clinical competence in hospital settings. Within the practicum, students will be trained to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in daily nursing practice. The training contents include practicing nursing routings, writing nursing records, familiar with nursing staff job descriptions, and participating in managing emergency situations. Students are expected to provide evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care based on assessment. Students will also be trained to communicate and cooperate with other medical team members, and to provide patients and their families health education and consultation. Students are also encouraged to actively participating in clinical and ethical issue discussions.','實習期間：02/19-04/03，修課限制：實習課程、本系四技一般生大四、畢業班課程、修課名單由護理系實習辦公室提供','第1~7週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','4','1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9','','L0',6),('983','臨床就業選習','Practicum for Obtaining Nursing Employment','本課程旨在培養學生整合並運用專業護理相關之知識與技能，於護理實務工作中，透過連續性且全時臨床護理實習，增加學生職場就業機會及提升工作適應能力，以奠定學生從事臨床護理工作的基礎。','The purpose of the course is to develop students’ clinical competence in hospital settings. Within the practicum, students will be trained to integrate and apply nursing theories, related knowledge, and skills in daily nursing practice. The training contents include practicing nursing routings, writing nursing records, familiar with nursing staff job descriptions, and participating in managing emergency situations. Students are expected to provide evidence-based, individualized, and prioritized nursing care based on assessment. Students will also be trained to communicate and cooperate with other medical team members, and to provide patients and their families health education and consultation. Students are also encouraged to actively participating in clinical and ethical issue discussions.','實習期間：02/19-04/03，修課限制：實習課程、本系四技一般生大四、畢業班課程、修課名單由護理系實習辦公室提供','第1~7週',1132,'11140','4','專業必修(系所)','5','1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9','','L0',6),('984','高等資料分析方法論','Advanced data analysis methods','本課程著眼於博士層級之量性資料分析理論與實務。主要是由以下課題：測度理論、廣義線性模式、抽樣分配、模型建立、高等相依資料處理等，選取適當課題，探討目前資料分析方法、實用觀念以及可行之技巧及工具，引導學生操作或使用SPSS和SAS等分析工具。透過本課程之講授和練習，可讓學生具備對介入性研究以及護理量性資料的分析能力，進一步能夠評估研究設計及相關推論之效能，並運用於研究與實務之專業上。','The focus of this course is applied statistical techniques, with emphasis on general linear model, sampling theory, model testing, longitudinal data analysis and multivariate analysis through the Statistical Package for the Social Sciences (SPSS) and the statistical analysis system (SAS). This course will complete weekly computer assignments that provide \"hands on\" experience with data analysis and interpretation of results. Students will actually understand statistical procedures and apply statistical techniques to concrete data.','修課限制：本所國內博士班、程式設計課程','全18週',1132,'11170','1','專業選修(系所)','4','10,11,12','F603','10',3),('985','高等質性研究方法論','Advanced Qualitative Research','此課程主要為質性研究方法論之介紹與練習，學生能了解質性研究之發展，典範\r\n與方法論，進而能運用質性研究練習收集資料，分析資料及批判質性研究，期使\r\n學生能有執行質性研究之專題經驗。課程內容包含：質性研究之典範，紮根理論，\r\n現象學，各類質性研究之比較，質性研究之收集資料，分析資料，嚴謹度，批判，\r\n撰寫等。','This course critically examines diverse qualitative approaches applied in research.\r\nThe discussion emphasizes on philosophical bases of qualitative inquiries, whereas\r\nthe analysis focuses on paradigmatic nature of qualitative approaches in contrast to\r\nquantitative approaches. The class presents sampling and a variety of data collection\r\nprocedures; discusses issues on rigor; explores methods of analysis appropriate to the\r\ndata; and considers ethical issues associated with each stage of the research. Students\r\nare expected to complete a qualitative project.','修課限制：本所國內博士班','全18週',1132,'11170','1','專業必修(系所)','4','2,3,4','B603','A0',3),('986','進階護理實務實習I','Advanced Nursing Practicum (Ι)','本課程旨在提供護理系博士班學生於健康或相關機構獲得實務或研究經驗。過程中\r\n提供學生機會藉由熟識臨床實務問題，分析和詮釋目前護理科學之發展，參與相關\r\n之實證或實務活動。','This course aims to provide nursing doctoral students to obtain clinical or research\r\nexperiences at health related institutions. Based on familiar with clinical issues, students will\r\nanalyze and interpret the current development of nursing science, involve the related practice.','修課限制：實習課程、本所國內博士班','全18週',1132,'11170','1','專業必修(系所)','4','5,6','B603','A0',2),('987','課程發展與設計','Curriculum Development','本課程主要在強化學生教學能力，是護理教育師資培育主要的起始點，課程內容包\r\n含(1) 分析課程發展的理論與過程；(2) 綜述及分析護理教育的演進及議題，來檢視護\r\n理教育者的角色與功能；(3)反思創意教學的策略與相關議題。本課程教學方法是強調自\r\n我導向、創意及批判性思考之能力培育。','This course examines the role of the nurse educator in both academic and health care settings.\r\nCurriculum development is analyzed, discussed, and evaluated. It could reflect current\r\nlearning theory, technology, healthcare delivery systems, social issues, and trend, and\r\nevidence-based studies.','1140220關課。修課限制：本所國內博士班博二以上','全18週',1132,'11170','2','專業選修(系所)','4','6,7','','20',2),('988','介入性與臨床試驗研究方法論','Design and Analysis of Nursing Intervention Studies','This course is designed to familiarize students with theory-driven nursing intervention reearch and clinical trials, including design, conduct, analysis and interpretation of results. Topics will include commonly used designs, methods for randomization, blinding and sample size determination, choice of controls, collaborative/ multicenter trial requirements and operational issues, data management and data quality issues, interim analysis methods, critical review of clinical trial results, ethics considerations and statistical techniques for analyzing clinical trial and nursing intervention data.','This course is designed to familiarize students with theory-driven nursing intervention reearch and clinical trials, including design, conduct, analysis and interpretation of results. Topics will include commonly used designs, methods for randomization, blinding and sample size determination, choice of controls, collaborative/ multicenter trial requirements and operational issues, data management and data quality issues, interim analysis methods, critical review of clinical trial results, ethics considerations and statistical techniques for analyzing clinical trial and nursing intervention data.','修課限制：本所博士班博二以上','全18週',1132,'11170','2','專業選修(系所)','4','2,3,4','B636','21',3),('989','論文專題研究I','Dissertation Independent Study I','本課程以個別指導之形式，依據博士生未來護理專業發展方向，引導學生探索護理實務相關之研究議題，進行相關理論及照護模式之分析，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，與產官學界等多方領域先進之討論，訂定研究方向及主題，擬定研究設計、進行或完成研究計畫之撰寫。','This course is conducted through individualized instruction and is designed to guide doctoral students in exploring research topics relevant to their future nursing professional development. It involves the analysis of pertinent theories and care models, integration of their clinical expertise, application of critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, and engagement in discussions with experts from various sectors including academia, industry, and government. The course aims to help the student determine his/her research direction and topic, formulate research designs, and initiate or complete the writing of a research proposal.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所國內博士班、書面選課','全18週',1132,'11170','2','專業選修(系所)','7','1','','A0',1),('99','休閒健康畢業專題','Final Project on Leisure and Health','本課程旨在協助學生對專題撰述之相關議題做更深入、完備之研討。研究生所選擇的問題主題將成為課程中的討論焦點。同儕間與師生間之腦力激盪、相互研討是本課程的主要學習策略。','This course aims at helping students to make deeper and more complete discussions on their final projects related to leisure and health. The topics of the projects will be chosen by students and will be the focus of the discussions in the class. The purpose of this course is to stimulate intellectual exchanges and communications between students and professors.','修課限制：\n1.本系四技一般生四年級、畢業班課程。\n2.未選修觀光休閒健康產業進階實習之同學，請務必選修畢業專題課程。\n3.第一次上課有安排教室F1006上課時間：13:30-17:00，第二周開始由指導老師個別指導及安排指導上課時間，無安排教室。','第1~14週',1132,'23140','4','專業選修(系所)','2','5','','40',3),('990','論文專題研究II','Dissertation Independent Study II','本課程以個別指導之形式，依據博士生未來護理專業發展方向，引導學生應用相關核心概念，發展護理相關理論及照護模式，結合其臨床專業技能，應用批判性思考及實證護理的概念，確認研究主題及設計、完成博士論文研究計畫之書寫。','This course is structured as individualized instruction, tailored to the doctoral student’s future development in the field of nursing. It guides the student to apply relevant core concepts, develop nursing-related theories and nursing care models, integrate his/her clinical expertise, employ critical thinking and evidence-based nursing concepts, and confirm his/her research topic and designs. It culminates in the completion of a written research proposal for his/her dissertation.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所國內博士班、書面選課','全18週',1132,'11170','2','專業選修(系所)','7','3','','A0',1),('991','博士論文I','Dissertation I','本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助博士生以臨床實務或護理專業發展為基礎，應用相關理論、照護模式及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析、研究成果報告發表及博士論文之撰寫。','This course is structured as individualized instruction with the aim of assisting the doctoral student who is building upon his/her clinical practice or nursing professional development. It emphasizes the application of relevant theories, nursing care models, and research skills, the execution of research projects, data analysis, publishing of the results of studies, and the writing of his/her dissertation.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所國內博士班、書面選課','全18週',1132,'11170','3','專業必修(系所)','7','2','','A0',6),('992','博士論文II','Dissertation II','本課程以個別指導之形式，旨在協助博士生以臨床實務或護理專業發展為基礎，應用相關理論、照護模式及研究能力，執行研究計畫，進行資料分析，完成博士論文之撰寫。','This course is conducted through individualized instruction with the objective of assisting the doctoral student who is building upon his/her clinical practice or nursing professional development. It focuses on the application of relevant theories, nursing care models, and research skills, the execution of research projects, data analysis, and the completion of the dissertation.','授課時間地點請洽指導教授，修課限制：本所國內博士班、書面選課','全18週',1132,'11170','3','專業必修(系所)','7','4','','A0',6),('993','資料庫設計與應用','Database Design and Application','本課程旨在培養學生對資料庫設計及其應用有基本概念，瞭解資料庫的基本概念、資料庫分析與設計的理論基礎及其使用軟體工具，藉由實際撰寫資料庫設計程式，能瞭解資料庫系統具有資料管理功能，同時也介紹資料庫管理系統於護理實務領域的應用狀況，讓學生體認資料庫設計概念於健康及護理實務領域的重要性。','This course will foster the student to have the basic concept of the database design and application. This course will assist students to understand the basic concepts of database systems, the theoretical basis of the analysis and design database and the application of software tools. Through the practice writing the program language of design database, students would understand database systems have data management functions. Also introduces database management system application status in the field of nursing practice. Through this course, students can recognize the concept of database management systems on the importance of the healthcare and nursing practice field.','修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）','全18週',1132,'11162','1','專業選修(系所)','5','8,9,10','F603','10',3),('994','中醫藥學：實務與研究','Traditional Chinese medicine: Practice and Research','本課程旨在培育學生具中醫藥基本知識之基礎知能及現代中醫(Modern TCM)進階科學化精神，課程設計以陰陽五行之觀念為基礎，並介紹八綱辨証, 經絡輸穴, 中醫疾病如何辨證及各種中醫手法等主題。以激發學生對中醫藥的興趣.','This program aims to nurture the professional ability of combining the TCM and Western Medical. Students have to use their knowledge of TCM and nursing, for example like physiological pathology、etiology、clinical diagnostics、physical assessment and management . Through the subject of Traditional Chinese medicine: Practice and Research, this program uses organized and systematic way to integration of theoretical and clinical practice, and implement the plans in the program. In this way, the professional ability of students could be strengthened, and fulfill the purpose of the program.','修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）、外所（是否列入畢業學分，請參照入學年課程科目表）、跨校','全18週',1132,'11162','1','專業選修(系所)','5','11,12,13','G103','11',3),('995','藥膳學與實驗','Nutrition in Chinese Medicine','藥膳學在中醫基礎理論指導下，將中草藥與食物相配伍，運用傳統之飲食烹調技術和現代加工方法製成味、色、形具佳的及更有保健和治療作用之食品，其內容廣泛，迄今已有三千年之歷史，所謂藥食同源更是集中而深刻的體現了藥膳之重要性，而其藥膳成分對於人體自律神經及自由基及體內自泌素之影響更是本科目之重點研究。本課程共分: 藥膳概論、穀物湯膳與研究、蔬菜湯膳與研究、果品湯膳與研究、畜肉湯膳與研究、海鮮湯膳與研究、藥草湯膳與研究和美容養生湯膳與研究從營養角度看食品安全問題、食品添加物的聰明選擇、自然食材及添加物的應用等.','This program aims to nurture the professional ability of combining the TCM and Western Medical. Students have to use their knowledge of TCM and nursing, for example like physiological pathology、etiology、clinical diagnostics、physical assessment and management . Through the subject of Nutrition in Chinese Medicine, this program uses organized and systematic way to integration of theoretical and clinical practice, and implement the plans in the program. In this way, the professional ability of students could be strengthened, and fulfill the purpose of the program.','修課限制：本所碩士班（成人組、老人組、婦女組、精神組、社區組、兒童組、護資組、專師組、中西醫組）、外所（是否列入畢業學分，請參照入學年課程科目表）、跨校','全18週',1132,'11162','1','專業選修(系所)','5','8,9,10','G103','12',2),('996','成人專科護理 I','Adult Practice Nursing I','本課程旨在培育成人專科護理師學生具備照護急性住院病人常見健康需求之進階知識與技能，並加強其對對專科護理師角色、功能與執業議題之瞭解。課程強調運用批判性思維與實證醫學和護理，以建立適當之健康問題診斷、處置和評價照護結果之學習。透過講述、學生課堂導讀、案例分析、小組討論、角色扮演、影片情境分析與數位平台討論等多元教學策略，訓練學生批判性思維考、溝通與自學能力，並培養學生具備成人專科護理師入門所需之知識與技能，使其能以專科護理師的角色提供急性住院病人適切之進階護理照護。','This course provides the student with in-depth knowledge of common clinical situations in acute care setting. The role and function of the acute care nurse practitioner will be integrated throughout the course. Emphasis is on the utilization of critical thinking and evidence-based practice to formulate diagnoses and management and evaluation plans of care for physiologically unstable adult patients who have health problems, and are at high risk for developing complications. The focus is on the management of specific system problems of acute care. This course provides students with fundamental knowledge necessary to deliver advanced nursing care in acute care settings.','02/05寒假提前上課。修課限制：本所碩士班（專師組）','全18週',1132,'11168','1','專業必修(系所)','5','5,6,7','F501','A0',3),('997','成人專科護理實習 I','Adult Practice Nursing I - Practicum','本實習課程旨在培育成人專科護理師學生，照護急性住院病人常見健康需求，展現入門之專科護理師角色與功能，應用進階之護理知識與技能於提供病情單純之成人病患照護，並對專科護理師常見之執業議題有初步瞭解。實習強調運用批判性思維與實證醫學和護理，以建立適當之健康問題診斷、處置和評價照護結果於所照護之個案。透過實習契約書之訂定、實習指導教師與實習教學教師的共同輔導、實習日誌、個案報告、互動記錄、鑑別診斷形成與問題解決過程報告、與實習心得的完成，以確保學生的實習經驗，至實習結束每位學生將至少照護十位內外科常見之急性住院病人，以培養學生具備成人專科護理師入門所需之知識與技能，使其能以專科護理師的角色提供病情單純之急性住院病人適切之進階護理照護。','This course provides the student to apply knowledge of advanced nursing management in acutely ill adults. Emphasis is on the utilization of critical thinking and evidence-based practice to formulate diagnoses and management and evaluation plans of care for physiologically unstable adult patients who have health problems, and are at high risk for developing complications. The focus is on the management of specific system problems of acute care. This course provides students to apply fundamental knowledge necessary to deliver advanced nursing care in acute care settings.','02/05寒假提前上課。修課限制：實習課程、本所碩士班（專師組）','全18週',1132,'11168','1','專業必修(系所)','6','14','','A0',3),('998','老人健康照護 I','Health Care of Elderly I','此課程旨在透過對老人老化及疾病相關之病理、生理、心理、情緒及靈性需求之理論、研究與議題研討，增進學生老人照護的臨床專業能力。學生需統整及應用老人疾病照護、經濟、主要照顧者、社會、組織、資源整合、臨終照護等理論研究於臨床實務中，發揮個案照護之功能，並需針對特定議題完成方案以展現其老人臨床照護專家的角色及功能。','This course in designed to assist students acquiring clinical expertise in the nursing care of healthy aging population with specified health problems. Theories, research, and issues relevant to normal developmental transitions and changes in aging will be discussed. Emphasis is placed on physiological, psychological, family-social-cultural-environmental, spiritual, and functional aspects related to nursing interventions with the healthy aging population. Students are expected to develop a preliminary conceptual model to explain a clinical phenomenon involving healthy aging and its implication in nursing.','修課限制：本所碩士班（老人組）','全18週',1132,'11162','1','專業必修(系所)','5','5,6,7','B111','A0',3),('999','老人健康照護實習 I','Health Care of Elderly I - Practicum ( 144hours )','此實習旨在透過對老化及疾病相關之生理、病理、心理社會及靈性需求之理論、並配合應用口述歷史進行老人生命回顧之研討，學生需同時統整及應用老人疾病照護、主要照顧者、社會組織、資源整合、臨終照護等理論於臨床實務中，發揮個案照護之功能。學生並透過自我導向之學習，於醫療照護機構及社區情境中完成獨立提供老人連續性健康照護，以期展現老人照護專業角色功能及實務能力。','This course in designed to assist students acquiring clinical expertise in the nursing care of healthy aging population with specified health problems. In this course, students are required to select a problem or an issue discussed in the seminar, and complete the nursing process through integration and application of the theories for selected clients in appropriate clinical settings. Students are expected to develop a preliminary conceptual model to explain a clinical phenomena involving aging and its implications in nursing. Problem solving and critical thinking skills of students will be enhanced by the teaching strategy in this course.','修課限制：實習課程、本所碩士班（老人組）','全18週',1132,'11162','1','專業必修(系所)','6','14','','A0',3);
